<h1>ui-backdrop</h1>

<p>
  <code>ui-backdrop</code> is a very simple component that is set
  to <code>position: fixed</code> and covers the whole screen.
</p>

<p>
  Together with the <code>ui-position</code> component, they form the
  basis on how <code>ember-ui-kit</code> manages z-index. Please
  refer to the {{#link-to "docs.architecture/z-index"}}z-index doc
  {{/link-to}} for details.
</p>

